just recently:

00:04:53.058 --> 00:04:54.459
"Alex through the Looking Glass -

00:04:54.659 --> 00:04:57.487
How Life Reflects Numbers
and Numbers Reflect Life".

00:04:57.687 --> 00:05:00.536
It's really good.
It's also just out in the US,

